    "name": "Bigfoot Life",
    "steam_appid": 3108130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Bigfoot Life》是一款轻松的第三人称模拟游戏，在这里你将化身为传说中的生物——大脚怪，探索、采集并照顾你所称之为家的森林。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫步于郁郁葱葱的森林，静静地在溪流中钓鱼，建造简易庇护所以度过季节的更替。运用神秘的力量治愈动物，维持自然的平衡。解锁新技能，邂逅其他生物，并以森林隐秘守护者的身份谱写属于自己的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供<strong>三种不同模式</strong>——<strong>普通模式</strong>、<strong>生存模式</strong>和<strong>自由模式</strong>，每种模式都有不同的节奏与挑战。无论你想要一段有目标的旅程、轻度的生存体验，还是完全自由的探索，《Bigfoot Life》都能适应你的游戏方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这并不是一款节奏紧凑的生存或动作游戏，而是一段宁静的、以探索和自然为核心的体验，展现大脚怪平凡而惬意的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/e7ac282d791043e976e8674f0b185c1b.poster.avif?t=1764079422\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/e7ac282d791043e976e8674f0b185c1b.webm?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/e7ac282d791043e976e8674f0b185c1b.mp4?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法概览</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创建你自己的大脚怪</strong> – 在冒险开始前自定义你的外观。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三种游戏模式：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>普通模式：</strong> 节奏平衡、需求轻松的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存模式：</strong> 更具挑战性，需要管理资源并适应季节变化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由模式：</strong> 没有目标和限制——自由探索，放松身心。</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索与采集</strong> – 在充满蘑菇、浆果与秘密的森林中自由探索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>钓鱼与觅食</strong> – 捕捉鱼类、小型动物并采集食物，维持自己与动物们的生计。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造与休息</strong> – 建立庇护所储存物品、休息并为冬天做好准备。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁大脚怪技能</strong> – 随着游戏进展获得强化视觉、力量及神秘能力等技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>治愈森林</strong> – 运用大脚怪的治愈之力帮助受伤的动物，恢复自然平衡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态季节与天气</strong> – 体验昼夜更替与四季变化的生机森林。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平和的邂逅</strong> – 与人类或其他大脚怪相遇——有的充满好奇，有的保持警惕。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>放松且非线性的体验</strong> – 没有强制目标或战斗。以自己的节奏探索，享受理想的大脚怪人生。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>重要说明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Bigfoot Life》适合希望放松身心、以自己的节奏探索、并与自然建立联系的玩家。<br>它并非为追求紧张刺激的生存体验而设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏专注于探索、轻度采集和环境叙事。<br><strong>不包含复杂的生存系统、基地建造或激烈的战斗。</strong><br>相反，它提供一种平和、冥想般的体验，聚焦于自然、独处与缓慢成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时间、天气和季节变化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/d517e0500f66c87ae3d0130845f8ed49.poster.avif?t=1764079422\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/d517e0500f66c87ae3d0130845f8ed49.webm?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/d517e0500f66c87ae3d0130845f8ed49.mp4?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>大脚怪技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/6a874842841cf6a234e734ac13cafc6e.poster.avif?t=1764079422\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/6a874842841cf6a234e734ac13cafc6e.webm?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/6a874842841cf6a234e734ac13cafc6e.mp4?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与其他大脚怪互动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/e1fdde1130f09b6ce99e50fb1cb9d750.poster.avif?t=1764079422\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/e1fdde1130f09b6ce99e50fb1cb9d750.webm?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108130/extras/e1fdde1130f09b6ce99e50fb1cb9d750.mp4?t=1764079422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
